To run the checker you need Python 3.8 or newer

Then open terminal ----------(windows +r -> type: cmd) or search in search box

Run the following commands so the script can work:

pip install requests

pip install colorama

Then u can double click the gumrs checker and it should work

------------------------- Discord Checker ( Dont Download "gumrs_checker.py" ) --------------------------------

After saving the checker, replace "YOUR_TOKEN_HERE" with your actual Discord Bot token if you want to use the Discord module.
                                                  (Not giving you my token)

Heres how to make a discord bot token: https://youtu.be/jqnul0VpBUQ?si=6-elE7GioCSvCnyj&t=6

Where do i put it? open "gumrs_checker.txt" click the 3 buttons on top right -> download
-> ctrl +f , then search token, replace this "YOUR_TOKEN_HERE" with your token 
-> then click file in notepad (top left) -> "save as" , any name [example (anyname.py) ]

Double Click the file and ur done 

